<a data-tip="p$t$yik-wang" href="/people/yik-wang">Yik Wang</a>，<strong title="Elementary Particle Theory" class="zu-question-my-bio">Elementary Particle Theory</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
